description: This file defines a Qwik component called RouterHead that is responsible for rendering HTML `<head>` contents dynamically based on the document head state and location. It imports Qwik and Qwik-City hooks and utilizes JSX to generate head elements like title, meta tags, links, styles, and scripts.

methods.name: RouterHead
methods.description: A Qwik component that renders dynamic head elements based on document head and location.
